â™« My joyful heart is restless because of the words left unspoken â™«

28
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:05,240
â™« It has to be you. Please, don't go â™«

29
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:08,270
â™« Touch me even without knowing the whole truth â™«

30
00:02:08,270 --> 00:02:12,110
â™« Just take in everything, everything, everything â™«

31
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:16,260
â™« Don't worry about getting burned â™«

32
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:21,180
â™« The reason why I wish to see a tomorrow that would stop my tears â™«

